Document: VisualShaderNodeColorFunc
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodecolorfunc.rst
Summary: Transforms input Color based on specified function in Visual Shader

Accepts a Color to the input port and transforms it according to the function property. The transformation is determined by the value of the function parameter, which specifies the color operation to apply.
